Xia Lin.

226
00:16:43,750 --> 00:16:46,910
Momentálne k tebe nič necítim.

227
00:16:46,990 --> 00:16:47,990
Ja viem.

228
00:16:48,350 --> 00:16:50,070
A preto som tu.

229
00:16:51,030 --> 00:16:52,350
Ah Ran mi povedala,

230
00:16:52,430 --> 00:16:55,270
