262
00:19:08,670 --> 00:19:10,830
Všade je samá ružová!

263
00:19:11,390 --> 00:19:15,670
Bože, také dievčenské!

264
00:19:22,310 --> 00:19:23,270
Pomaly.

265
00:19:30,870 --> 00:19:31,950
Si v poriadku?

266
00:19:41,070 --> 00:19:41,950
Yi Zhou.

267
00:19:44,230 --> 00:19:45,150
Stratil som rovnováhu.

268
00:19:46,910 --> 00:19:47,750
Pomôžem ti.

269
00:19:48,990 --> 00:19:50,190
Pomôžem mu.

270
00:19:51,150 --> 00:19:52,110
Som v poriadku, Ah Ran.

271
00:19:52,430 --> 00:19:54,150
Máš plné ruky,
tak jej dovoľ mi pomôcť.

272
00:20:01,390 --> 00:20:03,870
Yi Zhou, uvarila som ti polievku.

273
00:20:04,230 --> 00:20:07,590
Ešte nikdy som polievku nevarila,
takže nemusí chutiť najlepšie.

274
00:20:08,950 --> 00:20:10,150
Už jedol.

275
00:20:11,190 --> 00:20:12,590
Škoda!
Dlho som ju varila.

276
00:20:12,950 --> 00:20:13,790
Vyskúšam ju.

277
00:20:18,230 --> 00:20:19,230
Opatrne.

278
00:20:25,030 --> 00:20:26,070
Je dobrá.

279
00:20:26,550 --> 00:20:29,110
Ak ti chutí,
budem ti ju variť každý deň.

280
00:20:32,510 --> 00:20:35,350
To zvládnem aj ja.
Mala by si ísť do práce.

281
00:20:36,030 --> 00:20:37,190
Ja sa o Yi Zhou-a postarám.

282
00:20:38,830 --> 00:20:42,150
Xia Lin, som si istá,
že si teraz zaneprázdnená.

283
00:20:43,350 --> 00:20:44,190
Ako to myslíš?

284
00:20:44,510 --> 00:20:48,470
Po internete kolujú reči o tebe a Chu Yanovi.

285
00:20:48,990 --> 00:20:50,150
Ešte o tom nevieš?

286
00:20:50,390 --> 00:20:52,630
Aké reči?
O ničom neviem.

287
00:21:03,230 --> 00:21:05,950
"Bol Chu Yan na rande v hoteli?"

288
00:21:06,910 --> 00:21:09,470
"Chu Yan na rande so svojou tajnou priateľkou."

289
00:21:11,270 --> 00:21:13,470
Tí ľudia sa museli zblázniť.

290
00:21:24,310 --> 00:21:25,150
Áno?

291
00:21:25,430 --> 00:21:27,670
Xia Lin, okamžite sem príď.

292
00:21:30,310 --> 00:21:31,150
Dobre.

293
00:21:40,950 --> 00:21:42,870
Je tá fotka skutočná?

294
00:21:44,550 --> 00:21:45,590
Áno.

295
00:21:46,070 --> 00:21:47,150
Odkedy spolu chodíte?

296
00:21:47,390 --> 00:21:49,870
To je nedorozumenie.
Nechodíme spolu.

297
00:21:50,390 --> 00:21:54,390
Ten príbeh si vytvorili média.

298
00:21:54,830 --> 00:21:57,310
Prečo sa teda na teba pozeral s takou nehou?

299
00:21:58,030 --> 00:22:01,750
Je to iba pohľad.
Rovnako sa pozerá aj na psa.

300
00:22:03,470 --> 00:22:04,590
Xia Lin.

301
00:22:04,670 --> 00:22:06,950
Viem, že každá celebrita túži po sláve,

302
00:22:07,430 --> 00:22:10,870
