427
00:30:43,550 --> 00:30:46,510
Po našom prvom stretnutí...

428
00:30:47,230 --> 00:30:49,750
som dostala horúčku.

429
00:30:50,670 --> 00:30:52,030
A vieš prečo?

430
00:30:53,790 --> 00:30:56,270
Si zvedavý, však?

431
00:30:56,950 --> 00:30:58,190
Dostala som ju preto,

432
