435
00:31:16,190 --> 00:31:17,430
Páčia sa ti?

436
00:31:18,230 --> 00:31:22,310
Pripravila som ich špeciálne pre teba.

437
00:31:28,510 --> 00:31:29,350
Vypadni!

438
00:31:29,790 --> 00:31:31,630
Zober si tie veci a vypadni!

439
00:31:38,710 --> 00:31:42,070
<i>- 3. stratégia : falošný zármutok -</i>

440
00:31:48,390 --> 00:31:51,270
Bastard!

441
00:31:54,270 --> 00:31:56,590
Táto kniha je fakt na nič!

442
00:31:59,910 --> 00:32:02,270
36 spôsobov, ako zbaliť chlapa?
Blbosť!

443
00:32:03,950 --> 00:32:04,790
Nechajte ma.

444
00:32:06,230 --> 00:32:08,070
